\par \pard\plain \s21\sb0\sa120{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
Many cooking games focus on speed, optimization, or restaurant management. }{\*\cs16\i\ai\rtlch \ltrch\loch
Dapur Bonda}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 could instead celebrate }{\*\cs15\b\ab\rtlch \ltrch\loch
heritage, ritual, and memory}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
. The act of cooking becomes a tactile way to experience Malay culture, where recipes are not merely instructions but stories passed through generations.}
\par \pard\plain \s21\sb0\sa120{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
