 experience, it also has an unusual strength: players can cook on a desktop with a mouse or keyboard, then step directly into the same kitchen in VR without installing a native application. Given your experience with WebXR, interactive heritage, and stylized environmental storytelling, this concept aligns naturally with the kind of culturally grounded immersive experiences you've been developing.}
